  "wc.hero.subtitle": { en: "Your boss says \"file a report.\" Their insurance company says \"we'll handle it.\" What they're really saying is: \"we hope you don't call a lawyer.\"", es: "Su jefe dice \"llena un reporte.\" Su compañía de seguros dice \"nosotros nos encargamos.\" Lo que realmente están diciendo es: \"esperamos que no llame a un abogado.\"" },
